Quiz app

Educational project to conduct a sports research program due to the organizational and investigatory needs of the University

About

Brand: Quiz App

Location: Warsaw, Poland

Industry: Education

Budget:: $10,000 – $49,000

Clutch Review: 

5.0
 5/5

Product link: play.google.com/apps/testing/pl.edu.uw.timexcellence 

Type of software: Mobile App

Scope of work: Front-end, Back-end, UI/UX Design, Project Management, Quality Assurance

Quiz App is an application for the execution of the survey among respondents through the accomplishment of the quiz in order to inquire about past, present, and future effects of sports performance on their health and emotional state. The app will be used by athletes during the whole sport season, and then the customer will gather all data and draw conclusions for this research.

Technologies

PHP

React native

Laravel

TypeScript

Redux

react navigation

What our client
wanted

Tomasz Kurach

PhD Student & Sports Psychologist, University

We needed to develop a special app to conduct sport psychology research

Challenge

  • The main challenge was to implement integration with external platforms such as Qualtrics and Strava due to differences in APIs, data formats, and authentication mechanisms. Also, given the sensitive nature of athlete data, security was a top priority.

Key features

  • Track athletes’ physical and emotional states. The app will provide user authentication, personal profile management
  • Integration with Qualtrics for questionnaire and training assessment modules
  • Integration with Strava for training results, and a researcher-respondent panel for communication.

Project Team

Inna

Project Manager​

Yevhenii

Front-End Developer

Maria

QA

Vasyl

Back-End Developer

Kostya

Back-End Developer

Client’s review

Tomasz Kurach

PhD Student & Sports Psychologist, University

They always looked for solutions and responded quickly to any roadblocks. Should there be any complications, they managed to anticipate well and responded quickly. They were highly proactive – always looking for new solutions and responding to our needs.

5.0
 5/5

Business Value

We developed a mobile app in order to conduct a research program due to our organizational and investigatory needs to overcome the time-consuming problem of a manual paper survey and improve the process of the research in general. Our goal was to facilitate a user-friendly environment for all users and reduce manual effort

Let's start. It's easier than you think.

Contact us
